title: The industrial power supply market is anticipated to grow from an estimated USD 10.8 billion in 2022 to USD 14.5 billion in 2027, at a CAGR of 6.0%
The global plant-based meat market is estimated to be valued at USD 7.9 billion in 2022. It is projected to reach USD 15.7 billion by 2027, with a CAGR of 14.7%
